                            <b>Details of whether or not the patient presented a Gender Recognition Certificate. </b>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <b>This class is mandatory,  if the work item type being requested is investigateGender. It must not be present otherwise.</b>
                        </p>
                    </text>
