                            <b>Details or relevant information about the patient who is the subject of the duplicate as identified by the NHS number carried in the id of this class.</b>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <b>Referred to as the "duplicate patient" elsewhere in this tabular view</b>
                        </p>
                    </text>
                </otherAnnotation>
